{"tid":2070072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好重要] 希望你哋花少少時間入嚟睇 - 方舟移民系統","createTime":"2020-06-19T01:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T12:19:43.000Z","uid":267881,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c9ca67281d799f025a7a37f7fa12321087a541","tid":2070072,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T01:24:04.000Z","msg":"曾經連登有巴打提出過各種集體移民計劃<br />\n例如去開發人煙稀少嘅小國小鎮、買島<br />\n當時港人孤立無援先急住為前線鋪退路<br />\n時至今日，國際連線，攬炒進度漸見成果<br />\n我哋有能力諗得更大、更遠<br />\n<br />\n以前講移民係鳥獸散，冇系統性<br />\n而方舟計劃只係迫於無奈嘅緊急逃生路線<br />\n但自從英國、台灣放風接收港人之後<br />\n可以重新思考<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「方舟移民系統」</span>重點<br />\n- 有&rsquo;移民&rsquo;嘅質素，又有&rsquo;方舟&rsquo;嘅組織力<br />\n- 唔係撤退，係周詳戰略部署<br />\n- 係攬炒成功至到重生之間嘅必經階段<br />\n- 係達至攬炒成功嘅重要環節<br />\n- 門檻大大降低，可全民參與<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">何謂攬炒成功？</span><br />\nStep1 - 港人抗爭揭破中共真面目<br />\nStep2 - 外國勢力出師有名，打倒中共<br />\nStep3 - 香港進入英殖/美屬/獨立時代<br />\n而家進度係step2初段<br />\n但去到step2尾段就係最兇險嘅階段<br />\n因為中共會變成一條垂死猛獸極力反抗<br />\n首當其衝一定係風眼位：香港、香港人<br />\n佢會用盡一切不法手段反撲<br />\n例如大規模充公資產、處刑抗爭者<br />\n甚至在香港實施戰時法律、軍管<br />\n所以係嗰日之前一定要&rsquo;選擇性撤離&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">何謂選擇性撤離？</span><br />\n同遊行原理一樣，冇大台<br />\n所謂大台只係做協調，提供意見<br />\n每人都有自由選擇走唔走，走去邊<br />\n民意夠，計劃好，自然聚到人<br />\n不割蓆不分化<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">撤離過程點樣？</span><br />\nStep1 - 外國政府落實協助港人方案<br />\nStep2 - 以最大共識選取重點方舟城市<br />\nStep3 - 組織團隊協調港人適應<br />\nStep4 - 方舟市民守望相助，毋忘約定<br />\nStep5 - 探討和統籌成立新香港政府</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">方舟移民系統有咩用？</span><br />\n- 加強協調，有助適應、反攻<br />\n- 保護抗爭戰力，等待時機<br />\n- 帶走人才、資金，加速攬炒<br />\n- 加強對外宣傳（遊行、文宣）<br />\n- 藍絲走=加速攬炒，唔走=等炒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如何反攻？</span>我曾經提過一段歷史：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>1940年6月，法國向納粹德國投降，戴高樂逃亡至英國，號召法國人不要放棄希望，抵抗的火焰絕不會熄滅，這標誌了「自由法國」運動的開始。<br />\n邱吉爾決定承認戴高樂建立的自由法國流亡政府，而全球當時除了英國以外的國家，皆承認德國的傀儡政權為正式的法國政府，但在1941年蘇德戰爭爆發後，蘇聯也承認自由法國。日本偷襲珍珠港後，美國等其他同盟國同時也轉向支持自由法國政府。</em></span><br />\n等到中共再冇能力治港<br />\n新政府早已準備好接管<br />\n港共政權認授性歸零，等清算<br />\n香港重現三權分立、公正廉潔、自由民主<br />\n自然會吸引返手足回流<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人有冇咁團結？</span><br />\n- 不如問自己，你信唔信手足？<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2019/06/fb9263fd299c4c76b117d6e8d8ce0fbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2019%2F06%2Ffb9263fd299c4c76b117d6e8d8ce0fbd.jpg&h=064edcfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ECp5URaUIAEiGvm.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FECp5URaUIAEiGvm.jpg%3Alarge&h=b9305520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://samhighome.files.wordpress.com/2019/11/photo_2019-11-14-20.10.10.jpeg?w=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsamhighome.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F11%2Fphoto_2019-11-14-20.10.10.jpeg%3Fw%3D960&h=9e8c3a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phppNQKJm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phppNQKJm.jpg&h=c5a00728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我信<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一切由慨念開始<br />\n反復修正，改良，宣揚出去<br />\n就會成真<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考自<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 連登方舟計劃團隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299809</a><br />\n英國內政部公佈BNO新法案細節<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2066345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2066345</a><br />\n台灣「香港人道援助關懷行動專案」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2069195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2069195</a></span></em>"},{"pid":"fbe3f527a35ac6be2ca718923f2592b4fdbe29d8","tid":2070072,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a23f8929816ab12af373516cc9ba4b30e0b106","tid":2070072,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbe3f527a35ac6be2ca718923f2592b4fdbe29d8","tid":2070072,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e530f02c1613918c16d71e1c822f8557f6dde9","tid":2070072,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a23f8929816ab12af373516cc9ba4b30e0b106","tid":2070072,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbe3f527a35ac6be2ca718923f2592b4fdbe29d8","tid":2070072,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" 